    <item>
      <title>以色列对加沙地带的袭击造成数十名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/urgent-israeli-strikes-across-gaza-kill-dozens-of-palestinians-even-in-largely-emptied-north</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带代尔巴拉赫（美联社）以色列军队连夜轰炸加沙各地的城镇和难民营，直至周四，针对哈马斯的空中和地面攻势已造成数十人死亡，攻势已扩大到大部分领土，迫使数千人逃离家园和避难所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/urgent-israeli-strikes-across-gaza-kill-dozens-of-palestinians-even-in-largely-emptied-north</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 09:48:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其向美国寻求 F-16 发动机用于国产战斗机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/turkey-seeks-f-16-engines-from-us-to-use-in-domestic-warplane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其已请求美国允许联合生产用于 F-16 喷气式飞机的 GE 航空航天发动机，旨在将其部署到自己的国产战斗机上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/turkey-seeks-f-16-engines-from-us-to-use-in-domestic-warplane</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其浓雾中发生连锁反应碰撞，造成至少 10 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/chain-reaction-collision-in-dense-fog-on-turkish-motorway-leaves-at-least-10-people-dead-57-injured</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其安卡拉（美联社）——官员称，周四，土耳其西北部高速公路上发生了一起涉及七辆车的连锁反应事故，造成至少 10 人死亡、57 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/chain-reaction-collision-in-dense-fog-on-turkish-motorway-leaves-at-least-10-people-dead-57-injured</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 06:46:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港男子因挫败炸弹阴谋根据国安法被判入狱 6 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/hong-kong-man-jailed-for-6-years-after-pleading-guilty-to-a-terrorism-charge-over-a-foiled-bomb-plot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港（美联社）——周四，一名香港男子因参与未遂的爆炸法院大楼阴谋，根据北京实施的国家安全法承认犯有恐怖主义罪名，被判处六年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/hong-kong-man-jailed-for-6-years-after-pleading-guilty-to-a-terrorism-charge-over-a-foiled-bomb-plot</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 06:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾副总统满怀希望呼吁建立主权财富基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/taiwan-vice-presidential-hopeful-calls-for-sovereign-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾即将举行的选举中的一位副总统候选人在呼吁货币当局允许使用其数十亿美元的外汇储备中的一部分来设立主权财富基金后，正与强大的中央银行发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/taiwan-vice-presidential-hopeful-calls-for-sovereign-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 05:51:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列受伤士兵人数不断增加是战争的隐性成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-28/the-number-of-wounded-israeli-soldiers-is-mounting-representing-a-hidden-cost-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列拉马特甘（美联社）——伊戈尔·图多兰 (Igor Tudoran) 在加沙地带只呆了 12 个小时，一枚导弹就击中了他的坦克，导致他受了致命的伤。]]></description>
